正撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a7ad41d57201563de01f9ca964944ea4e481be","tid":464983,"uid":43963,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市面上，大部份都一定係冷藏然後整熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想食正既，自己去買條鱔，然後自己燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係試過自己燒 好撚正 係衰係個汁度😂<br />\n同埋啲骨大條好多"},{"pid":"455de8b4cc89f12d77cdae656a7428ff3400505d","tid":464983,"uid":18548,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/191316_50aac9436cd8f9cbbc923cc007badaab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F191316_50aac9436cd8f9cbbc923cc007badaab.jpg&h=ec08acd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩食緊鰻魚飯，見到個post"},{"pid":"3a6b81fb1dc1105fdeca8494015cea230cd985e9","tid":464983,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a2b347bbc47baff83ae6748dcaec0bd3e32580c","tid":464983,"uid":106026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係成田食過即劏鰻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成田有間好似叫豐川，係門口即劏即燒，真係正撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n川豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d23fb51d9c020c85593aff020fc82eef6cc6dd6","tid":464983,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平鰻魚飯一定腥過西咁</blockquote><br />\n荃灣一間平價餐廳，我自己做過，60蚊一個鰻魚飯真心幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老板仲係日本人.......雖然好似唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b09884332588e101fb867120758b73c20837ed0","tid":464983,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dbe4af621c0411b4f1f82528cb39f833f96735f","tid":464983,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:58:26.000Z","msg":"屌你 大撚把啦 唔識搵咋話<br />\ntenkuni<br />\nnadaman<br />\n鹿悅<br />\nronin<br />\n<br />\n紅磡三河屋呀東京食堂個啲都唔好再拎出黎講<br />\n仲有大大條淨係得個size都係垃圾<br />\napm新開打正旗號食鰻魚個間都係好一般<br />\n係香港地無300蚊都唔好諗住食到日本水平"},{"pid":"7a47b2a5a9b6893577e9f90c6f4dfe2c118b957a","tid":464983,"uid":44814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平鰻魚飯一定腥過西咁</blockquote><br />\n荃灣一間平價餐廳，我自己做過，60蚊一個鰻魚飯真心幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老板仲係日本人.......雖然好似唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和食快餐都不了 普通貨色<br />\n60蚊個啲周街都係"},{"pid":"1632daa48ee900941a43fc4a039ccd3e5da4e648","tid":464983,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"之前係灣仔食過一間好正<br />\nD魚油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩舊水左右 依家好似執左"},{"pid":"f52335d1b22eae1c7e8bd20e36af80bed9268fce","tid":464983,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平鰻魚飯一定腥過西咁</blockquote><br />\n荃灣一間平價餐廳，我自己做過，60蚊一個鰻魚飯真心幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老板仲係日本人.......雖然好似唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和食快餐都不了 普通貨色<br />\n60蚊個啲周街都係</blockquote><br />\n我覺得60蚊黎講，和食快餐真心超值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我食過丼丼屋, 一d中級既日式餐廳，鰻魚飯可能100-2xx, 懶係勁咁送個茶比你鰻魚泡飯個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d鰻魚太薄搞到好乾又鞋，有d又唔夠軟綿，真係和食都贏哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21917ed65ff434ff40af538a5c3ac7f770b324d7","tid":464983,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平鰻魚飯一定腥過西咁</blockquote><br />\n荃灣一間平價餐廳，我自己做過，60蚊一個鰻魚飯真心幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老板仲係日本人.......雖然好似唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和食快餐都不了 普通貨色<br />\n60蚊個啲周街都係</blockquote><br />\n我覺得60蚊黎講，和食快餐真心超值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我食過丼丼屋, 一d中級既日式餐廳，鰻魚飯可能100-2xx, 懶係勁咁送個茶比你鰻魚泡飯個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d鰻魚太薄搞到好乾又鞋，有d又唔夠軟綿，真係和食都贏哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只可以話係60蚊質素 <br />\n但係距離好食仲爭好遠 因為佢個啲都係批返黎嘅鰻魚<br />\n食材永遠都係一分錢一分貨"},{"pid":"b7e3c8d53ec222fe609510047dfb3500db626f23","tid":464983,"uid":3128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 大撚把啦 唔識搵咋話<br />\ntenkuni<br />\nnadaman<br />\n鹿悅<br />\nronin<br />\n<br />\n紅磡三河屋呀東京食堂個啲都唔好再拎出黎講<br />\n仲有大大條淨係得個size都係垃圾<br />\napm新開打正旗號食鰻魚個間都係好一般<br />\n係香港地無300蚊都唔好諗住食到日本水平</blockquote><br />\n睇你嗰名都知你食開日本高級嘢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec049aa26b5388cc2a4f40dd50c285cfea60ccf","tid":464983,"uid":71358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyT